WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.259 --> 01:37.872
=Episode 38=

02:21.616 --> 02:22.377
Someone!

02:23.057 --> 02:23.856
Help!

02:26.176 --> 02:26.856
Your Majesty!

02:26.937 --> 02:28.377
What's wrong, Your Majesty?

02:29.257 --> 02:30.016
Someone!

02:30.416 --> 02:31.537
Your Majesty!

02:32.257 --> 02:33.057
Your Highness,

02:33.257 --> 02:35.497
there's noise
from the Empress Dowager's chamber.

02:35.937 --> 02:36.696
Someone!

02:38.057 --> 02:39.057
Hurry up!

02:39.576 --> 02:41.337
Get out, you wretched creature!

02:42.377 --> 02:43.497
Drive it over there!

02:44.456 --> 02:45.257
Get out!

02:47.736 --> 02:48.537
Move aside!

02:51.097 --> 02:51.792
Move now!

02:51.792 --> 02:52.456
Get it out!

02:52.456 --> 02:53.377
Get it out!

02:55.576 --> 02:56.377
Hurry!

02:58.777 --> 02:59.937
Thank you, Princess Ding.

03:06.777 --> 03:07.576
Your Majesty.

03:13.176 --> 03:13.977
Your Majesty,

03:15.136 --> 03:16.537
that creature came out of nowhere

03:16.537 --> 03:17.497
and startled you.

03:17.497 --> 03:19.856
I've sent people
to inspect every opening in the palace,

03:19.856 --> 03:21.456
and I've doubled the night patrols.

03:21.456 --> 03:22.896
It shall never happen again.

03:25.777 --> 03:26.576
Alright.

03:27.456 --> 03:28.657
The weather turns warm.

03:28.896 --> 03:29.937
It just strayed in.

03:31.136 --> 03:31.977
You may leave.

03:33.296 --> 03:34.097
Yes.

03:42.296 --> 03:43.136
Have a seat.

03:54.296 --> 03:55.576
When I was young,

03:55.856 --> 03:57.537
I experienced a terrible drought.

03:58.576 --> 04:00.736
The court imposed heavy taxes
at that time,

04:01.257 --> 04:03.696
taking away the last of the grain seeds
needed for survival.

04:04.257 --> 04:05.657
The people had nothing to eat.

04:06.257 --> 04:08.337
The grass roots and tree bark
were long gone.

04:08.977 --> 04:10.576
Everything that could be eaten,

04:10.977 --> 04:12.136
be it birds, beasts,

04:12.497 --> 04:13.977
snakes, or bugs,

04:14.136 --> 04:15.537
was taken too.

04:17.137 --> 04:18.296
I have heard

04:19.376 --> 04:20.577
since His Majesty ascended,

04:21.056 --> 04:22.457
with your help in governance,

04:22.977 --> 04:25.137
the court decreed
the Disaster Year Tax Reduction.

04:25.496 --> 04:27.056
When disaster hits, relief comes first

04:27.296 --> 04:29.217
with taxes cut and granaries opened.

04:29.736 --> 04:30.856
Countless have been saved.

04:31.376 --> 04:33.977
Your governance speaks of true virtue.

04:37.416 --> 04:38.736
I often think to myself,

04:39.537 --> 04:41.697
although the drought that year
was a natural disaster,

04:42.856 --> 04:44.897
the dead were piled up everywhere.

04:45.577 --> 04:47.017
Wasn't it also a man-made calamity?

04:48.416 --> 04:50.376
Farmers toil all year round,

04:50.616 --> 04:51.936
but they can't feed themselves.

04:52.416 --> 04:53.537
They pay their taxes

04:53.856 --> 04:56.337
but receive no protection
in times of disaster.

04:57.457 --> 04:59.416
Where exactly does the crux

04:59.856 --> 05:01.217
of all these problems lie?

05:03.856 --> 05:05.017
You perceive clearly.

05:06.416 --> 05:07.577
The people's misery

05:08.256 --> 05:09.977
comes not just from nature's whims

05:10.856 --> 05:13.217
but more from deep-seated systemic flaws

05:13.736 --> 05:14.856
and official corruption.

05:15.657 --> 05:17.337
You reformed the tax system,

05:17.616 --> 05:18.616
purged corrupt officials,

05:18.936 --> 05:19.936
and initiated waterworks,

05:20.416 --> 05:21.816
a true service to the people.

05:22.697 --> 05:23.496
However,

05:25.176 --> 05:26.416
even the greatest merits

05:27.457 --> 05:29.537
cannot outweigh innocent deaths

05:29.977 --> 05:31.537
and lifelong grief.

05:32.376 --> 05:33.736
Merits and faults are distinct.

05:34.217 --> 05:35.337
The justice in this world

05:35.856 --> 05:38.176
has never been simply
weighing merits against faults.

05:50.217 --> 05:51.217
A few days ago,

05:51.977 --> 05:53.176
Duke Hua entered the palace

05:53.856 --> 05:55.816
and asked me if the Lishan tragedy

05:56.217 --> 05:58.056
was my doing.

05:59.537 --> 06:00.577
Don't tell me

06:01.897 --> 06:03.256
you think the same way.

06:06.176 --> 06:07.296
The people of Lishan

06:07.977 --> 06:09.376
did die of an acute illness.

06:10.416 --> 06:12.017
They also died by their own obsessions.

06:13.416 --> 06:14.736
However, the three-year blockade

06:15.217 --> 06:16.376
lacking in food and medicine

06:16.816 --> 06:17.936
is also a fact.

06:20.296 --> 06:21.697
Are you blaming me?

06:22.816 --> 06:24.017
Everyone has their own path.

06:25.097 --> 06:26.577
The same was true for Lishan.

06:28.137 --> 06:29.296
Once the path was chosen,

06:30.337 --> 06:31.777
they had to bear its consequences.

06:35.856 --> 06:36.977
You should know

06:37.977 --> 06:39.977
that your mother was my dearest friend,

06:41.256 --> 06:42.457
and Master Qingyun

06:42.936 --> 06:44.256
was my honored master.

06:45.577 --> 06:46.697
After leaving Lishan,

06:47.457 --> 06:48.657
I was full of fervent hope,

06:49.457 --> 06:50.897
desiring to cleanse the murky world.

06:53.736 --> 06:54.657
But

06:55.977 --> 06:57.176
as vast as the world was,

06:57.977 --> 07:00.097
where was the sky for a woman
to spread her wings?

07:02.376 --> 07:03.856
With no path for me in the court,

07:04.376 --> 07:05.777
I entered the palace directly,

07:06.256 --> 07:07.977
determined to carve out

07:08.537 --> 07:10.936
a path of transformation
here at the summit of power.

07:13.697 --> 07:14.897
You have lofty ambition.

07:15.337 --> 07:16.457
I deeply admire.

07:17.577 --> 07:20.296
Transformation indeed
requires great courage.

07:20.936 --> 07:22.296
Yet between gain and loss,

07:22.977 --> 07:24.697
the scales are not easily balanced.

07:29.777 --> 07:32.137
What do you think I have lost?

07:32.736 --> 07:34.097
Only your heart can answer that.

07:35.217 --> 07:36.457
My grandfather said

07:37.137 --> 07:38.816
that every single thing one does

07:39.137 --> 07:40.537
and every step one takes in life

07:40.936 --> 07:42.296
has its own gain and loss.

07:46.097 --> 07:48.416
Before Master Qingyun passed away,

07:48.897 --> 07:50.097
did he leave any final words?

07:52.657 --> 07:54.176
My grandfather fell ill too suddenly,

07:54.816 --> 07:55.856
leaving no last words.

08:08.537 --> 08:09.657
But I remember,

08:10.296 --> 08:11.496
during a Mid-Autumn Festival,

08:12.256 --> 08:13.897
after my grandfather had some wine,

08:14.296 --> 08:15.736
he was pacing beneath the moonlight,

08:16.697 --> 08:18.296
reciting two lines of poetry:

08:19.496 --> 08:21.736
"May the moonlight reach every corner,

08:22.496 --> 08:25.176
so all may live
in brightness and peace."

08:26.936 --> 08:29.256
Was it the poem I wrote in my youth?

08:32.376 --> 08:33.177
Yes.

08:34.536 --> 08:35.856
My grandfather once said

08:36.616 --> 08:38.097
the poem is bold in vision

08:38.536 --> 08:39.736
and deep in compassion,

08:40.297 --> 08:41.337
a fine piece indeed.

08:43.496 --> 08:44.536
But he also said

08:45.417 --> 08:48.217
that the highest truths
are easier to know than to follow.

08:49.057 --> 08:50.576
Just like the moon hangs high

08:51.117 --> 08:52.297
and shines upon all,

08:52.896 --> 08:54.217
yet across the vast land,

08:54.856 --> 08:56.496
every hill has its own shadow.

08:57.337 --> 08:59.937
If one's original intention
cannot be consistently upheld,

09:00.457 --> 09:01.496
the spirit in the poem

09:02.536 --> 09:04.457
will be no more than a castle on paper

09:05.496 --> 09:06.736
or the moon in a pond.

09:16.536 --> 09:17.337
Your Highness,

09:19.337 --> 09:20.577
Li Duo has ended his own life.

09:21.656 --> 09:22.496
Early in the battle,

09:22.496 --> 09:24.776
Mo Jingli fled with his elite troops.

09:25.577 --> 09:27.297
If they go into hiding like this,

09:27.616 --> 09:29.256
I am afraid we won't find them soon.

09:31.496 --> 09:33.297
He won't hide like this forever.

09:34.217 --> 09:36.977
Pass my order! Make sure to find him!

09:37.217 --> 09:38.016
Yes!

09:44.417 --> 09:45.217
Your Majesty!

09:46.616 --> 09:47.417
Your Majesty!

09:48.097 --> 09:48.937
A great victory!

09:49.297 --> 09:50.496
A victory at Luoxia Pass!

09:51.057 --> 09:53.177
Prince Ding set an ambush
at Jueyun Brook,

09:53.217 --> 09:54.977
wiping out Mo Jingli's main rebel force.

09:55.337 --> 09:56.656
Mo Jingli is on the run.

09:56.656 --> 09:58.337
They are currently pursuing him.

10:11.376 --> 10:12.697
How many men do we have left?

10:16.256 --> 10:17.057
Your Highness,

10:17.457 --> 10:19.536
we've only got
about 300 to 400 elite men with us.

10:19.536 --> 10:20.217
However,

10:20.217 --> 10:22.057
quite a few of our troops are scattered.

10:22.057 --> 10:23.297
If we can rally them all,

10:23.697 --> 10:24.817
our numbers can be larger.

10:28.856 --> 10:29.656
Your Highness,

10:29.977 --> 10:31.656
Prince Ding has captured
many of our men.

10:31.656 --> 10:33.496
He's still leading a massive manhunt.

10:33.776 --> 10:34.697
Secret scouts report

10:34.817 --> 10:37.256
that their search perimeter
is closing in on this area.

10:37.536 --> 10:38.297
I am afraid...

10:46.536 --> 10:48.097
Search for our remaining men.

10:48.856 --> 10:49.937
Get ready to move.

10:52.817 --> 10:53.616
- Yes.
- Yes.

10:57.896 --> 10:59.417
Your Highness, right over there.

12:14.817 --> 12:15.616
Are you alright?

12:19.376 --> 12:20.376
The conditions are crude.

12:20.977 --> 12:21.776
Just

12:22.297 --> 12:23.376
have a bite.

12:36.297 --> 12:37.097
Your Highness,

12:37.417 --> 12:38.616
the taro is really delicious.

12:38.937 --> 12:39.977
You should try some too.

12:41.856 --> 12:42.697
You eat it.

12:43.896 --> 12:44.736
I have more here.

13:06.217 --> 13:07.577
One summer,

13:08.297 --> 13:09.776
the weather was really hot.

13:10.817 --> 13:12.217
Father took us out to play.

13:13.577 --> 13:16.217
Ye Li and I planned to go to the lake
to pick lotus roots.

13:17.817 --> 13:20.376
There were huge red carp in the lake.

13:20.977 --> 13:22.616
Both of us scrambled to see them.

13:23.697 --> 13:24.977
The boat was rocking violently.

13:25.577 --> 13:27.536
I accidentally bumped into her.

13:28.817 --> 13:29.697
And she actually

13:29.856 --> 13:32.136
fell into the lake with a splash.

13:34.577 --> 13:37.217
She stubbornly insisted
that I apologize.

13:38.457 --> 13:39.297
I refused.

13:39.977 --> 13:41.297
I didn't do it on purpose.

13:42.136 --> 13:45.057
She was just floating
on the water like a duck.

13:45.536 --> 13:46.736
She swam and swam.

13:47.616 --> 13:49.177
In the end, she swam ashore by herself.

13:50.616 --> 13:52.217
After we got back, she caught a cold

13:55.457 --> 13:56.817
and sneezed for a very long time.

14:03.417 --> 14:04.736
Why are you telling me this?

14:12.937 --> 14:14.057
I am not smart,

14:15.697 --> 14:16.977
and I'm not good with words.

14:19.616 --> 14:20.776
I thought about it.

14:22.616 --> 14:24.496
In all the time I have been
with Your Highness,

14:25.577 --> 14:27.977
it seems like only when I
talk about that thing

14:29.057 --> 14:30.856
does Your Highness
seem a little happier.

14:36.536 --> 14:37.697
(Do you remember things)

14:37.856 --> 14:39.937
(from your childhood?)

14:40.417 --> 14:41.656
I recall one incident.

14:42.057 --> 14:42.736
One year,

14:42.896 --> 14:44.697
we spent months together in Hangzhou.

14:45.337 --> 14:47.337
The weather was quite hot.

14:47.656 --> 14:49.337
(We decided to charter a boat)

14:49.337 --> 14:50.992
(to pick lotus roots in the lake.)

14:51.136 --> 14:53.417
Enormous red carp swam beneath!

14:53.577 --> 14:55.536
Like this big!

14:55.937 --> 14:57.656
Both Ye Li and I leaned over to see,

14:58.057 --> 14:59.337
but the boat rocked violently.

14:59.536 --> 15:01.496
I accidentally bumped into her,

15:02.136 --> 15:05.016
(and she tumbled right into the lake.)

15:05.297 --> 15:06.457
(Such a ridiculous sight.)

15:06.457 --> 15:08.577
(She bobbed like a duck on the surface.)

15:09.016 --> 15:10.376
(She persistently)

15:10.376 --> 15:11.697
(demanded an apology, though.)

15:12.097 --> 15:13.417
(Guess what happened next?)

15:13.417 --> 15:15.217
She caught a chill afterwards,

15:19.417 --> 15:20.656
sneezing endlessly.

15:30.496 --> 15:31.297
Your Highness,

15:35.937 --> 15:37.297
to see you again

15:39.177 --> 15:39.977
is wonderful.

15:54.937 --> 15:56.697
Didn't you say it'd just be a few days?

15:56.697 --> 15:58.297
Why were you delayed for so long?

15:58.656 --> 16:00.697
Her Majesty kept me for a few more days.

16:01.136 --> 16:02.417
Is everything alright at home?

16:02.417 --> 16:03.057
Yes.

16:03.057 --> 16:03.977
Everything is well.

16:04.217 --> 16:06.656
You're back safe.
That's all that matters.

16:07.177 --> 16:09.217
Steward Cui, go prepare lunch.

16:09.697 --> 16:10.457
Yes.

16:11.457 --> 16:13.656
Your complexion looks quite good.

16:14.057 --> 16:15.057
Indeed, it does.

16:15.136 --> 16:16.217
The palace is nurturing.

16:16.217 --> 16:18.457
I even feel like
I have gained a little weight.

16:19.457 --> 16:21.536
Aunt, now that you're back,
you're staying, right?

16:22.097 --> 16:23.217
I can't say for sure.

16:30.256 --> 16:31.417
Your Highness, you're back.

16:36.417 --> 16:37.097
Li,

16:37.177 --> 16:38.417
you have no idea.

16:38.417 --> 16:39.297
These past few days,

16:39.297 --> 16:41.097
the palace rewards have been non-stop.

16:41.177 --> 16:42.177
It's because Xiuyao

16:42.177 --> 16:43.977
won another big victory
on the battlefield.

16:44.656 --> 16:46.097
His Majesty was extremely pleased.

16:46.417 --> 16:47.977
These days, the palace

16:47.977 --> 16:49.656
hasn't stopped sending rewards.

16:49.736 --> 16:52.256
Look at your room.
It can barely hold any more.

16:53.136 --> 16:55.177
Steward Cui is having
everything catalogued.

16:55.177 --> 16:55.977
Look,

16:56.136 --> 16:57.616
they can barely keep up.

16:58.536 --> 16:59.856
And look at that fabric.

16:59.856 --> 17:01.177
It is truly dazzling.

17:03.856 --> 17:06.217
Wash up first,
and we will have lunch soon.

17:07.857 --> 17:08.697
Right,

17:08.857 --> 17:11.056
I put the letter from Yao for you here.

17:11.657 --> 17:12.457
Thank you, Ms. Wen.

17:13.617 --> 17:14.417
Wuyou,

17:14.417 --> 17:15.096
let's go.

17:22.697 --> 17:23.496
(Li,)

17:24.137 --> 17:25.296
(read this as if we met.)

17:25.977 --> 17:27.256
(Your letter reached me.)

17:27.857 --> 17:28.937
(Reading it over)

17:29.457 --> 17:30.576
(eases my heart somewhat.)

17:31.857 --> 17:32.937
(The frontier is bitter,)

17:33.377 --> 17:34.457
(especially so lately.)

17:35.617 --> 17:37.857
(A few days ago, a light sleet fell.)

17:38.377 --> 17:39.457
(Though not a chi deep,)

17:39.736 --> 17:43.016
(the roads became muddy,
making travel difficult)

17:43.457 --> 17:44.816
(and adding to our troubles)

17:45.177 --> 17:46.417
(amid the ceaseless march.)

17:47.937 --> 17:49.697
(I wonder how the climate is
in the capital)

17:50.096 --> 17:51.096
(and how your health is.)

17:52.457 --> 17:54.657
(Two days past,
we chased rebels to Cang Ridge,)

17:55.137 --> 17:56.617
(and I chanced upon a strange fruit.)

17:57.056 --> 17:58.217
(It was blood crimson)

17:58.457 --> 17:59.617
(and glistened brilliantly.)

18:00.296 --> 18:02.417
(Jin picked it and ate it.)

18:03.096 --> 18:04.137
(Its taste was peculiar,)

18:04.816 --> 18:07.617
(a mix of sourness and astringency
with an earthy flavor.)

18:08.217 --> 18:09.697
(Upon asking the local elders,)

18:09.977 --> 18:12.137
(they said this fruit
is called 'Red Pearl,')

18:13.177 --> 18:14.417
(and they brew wine with it.)

18:15.217 --> 18:16.736
(Thinking of your curious nature,)

18:17.377 --> 18:19.377
(you might wish to taste it.)

18:19.857 --> 18:21.377
(I ordered Jin to get two jars of it.)

18:22.096 --> 18:23.417
(Once the dust settles,)

18:24.016 --> 18:26.417
(I will have a swift horse
deliver it to the capital.)

18:28.457 --> 18:29.217
(Li,)

18:30.256 --> 18:31.336
(being away too long,)

18:32.056 --> 18:33.137
(my longing for you)

18:33.816 --> 18:34.937
(deepens daily.)

18:36.177 --> 18:37.336
(My feelings for you)

18:37.816 --> 18:38.857
(are deeper than ever.)

18:40.177 --> 18:41.296
(Please take care.)

18:42.177 --> 18:44.016
(Please do.)

18:57.617 --> 19:00.096
Greetings, Your Majesty.

19:01.296 --> 19:02.056
Please rise, Duke.

19:03.496 --> 19:04.080
Alright.

19:04.776 --> 19:05.457
Duke,

19:06.377 --> 19:07.816
I overheard your conversation

19:08.056 --> 19:09.217
with my mother that day.

19:09.897 --> 19:10.736
These past few days,

19:10.977 --> 19:12.776
I haven't slept a single peaceful night.

19:12.977 --> 19:14.457
I repeatedly question myself

19:15.256 --> 19:17.056
whether I'm worthy or not.

19:19.816 --> 19:20.617
Your Majesty,

19:22.056 --> 19:23.256
past matters,

19:23.816 --> 19:26.336
whatever twists and darkness
they may hide,

19:27.336 --> 19:29.657
all old wounds and festering sores.

19:30.177 --> 19:32.137
What our country needs now

19:32.657 --> 19:34.816
is not for Your Majesty
to dwell on the past,

19:34.816 --> 19:38.056
repeatedly seeking answers
and feeling guilt.

19:38.457 --> 19:39.617
The state

19:40.457 --> 19:43.217
cannot withstand another upheaval.

19:45.617 --> 19:46.457
Please sit, Duke.

19:47.696 --> 19:48.296
Alright.

19:51.056 --> 19:51.937
But Duke,

19:53.336 --> 19:54.736
if I am truly incompetent

19:55.137 --> 19:56.816
and ultimately unfit to be a ruler,

19:57.417 --> 19:58.457
then even with remorse,

19:58.816 --> 19:59.857
it benefits none.

20:00.457 --> 20:02.177
I am so muddled and incompetent.

20:02.697 --> 20:04.177
I listened to Li Duo's slander,

20:04.617 --> 20:06.857
causing the military authority
at Suixue Pass to be lost.

20:07.736 --> 20:09.697
I even repeatedly suspected Prince Ding,

20:10.177 --> 20:12.137
chilling the hearts
of the loyal and the able.

20:13.457 --> 20:15.816
That Your Majesty can speak these words

20:17.296 --> 20:18.657
actually makes me

20:19.536 --> 20:21.417
feel suddenly gratified.

20:23.137 --> 20:24.096
This shows

20:25.776 --> 20:27.776
that Your Majesty
has a scale in your heart,

20:29.457 --> 20:31.816
weighing the gravity of the state

20:32.536 --> 20:33.576
and measuring

20:33.576 --> 20:35.536
the gains and losses
of a ruler's virtue.

20:39.137 --> 20:40.056
Gains and losses?

20:41.697 --> 20:44.217
But I only see loss, not gain.

20:45.296 --> 20:46.816
I lost a strategic pass

20:47.857 --> 20:49.457
and the trust of my army.

20:49.697 --> 20:51.217
Even more, I lost the clear judgment

20:51.536 --> 20:52.857
a ruler should possess.

20:56.816 --> 20:57.897
Your Majesty,

20:59.576 --> 21:00.377
do you know

21:01.016 --> 21:03.016
that when the late emperor
first took the throne,

21:03.457 --> 21:05.977
he also misjudged
the situation at the border,

21:06.576 --> 21:08.657
resulting in the loss of three cities?

21:09.217 --> 21:10.617
At that time, the late emperor,

21:11.217 --> 21:13.776
just as Your Majesty is now,

21:14.857 --> 21:17.457
confined himself to the inner palace

21:17.977 --> 21:19.336
and missed court for three days.

21:20.736 --> 21:21.617
My father...

21:22.096 --> 21:22.977
Indeed.

21:24.336 --> 21:25.576
The late Empress Dowager

21:26.177 --> 21:27.857
asked the late emperor one question:

21:28.857 --> 21:33.016
"Would Your Majesty rather
spend three days here in self-reproach

21:33.977 --> 21:35.137
or

21:36.256 --> 21:40.016
spend thirty years governing diligently,

21:41.177 --> 21:44.177
in exchange
for a peaceful and tranquil realm?"

21:55.977 --> 21:56.776
Your Majesty,

21:58.377 --> 21:59.377
just now,

22:00.217 --> 22:01.096
you asked

22:01.417 --> 22:02.536
whether you were worthy.

22:02.897 --> 22:06.137
I will answer you frankly.

22:07.336 --> 22:08.977
That Your Majesty is here today,

22:09.857 --> 22:11.417
worrying for your ministers,

22:12.217 --> 22:14.857
feeling guilt towards your officials,

22:15.336 --> 22:18.776
and reflecting on your faults
for the sake of the realm

22:20.657 --> 22:21.336
is

22:22.536 --> 22:24.977
the very foundation of being worthy.

22:33.016 --> 22:34.096
Thank you, Duke.

22:35.217 --> 22:36.137
Your Majesty.

22:40.576 --> 22:41.736
I am young and inexperienced.

22:42.496 --> 22:44.056
I still need the support of my elders.

22:45.016 --> 22:47.137
I earnestly request
that you stay by my side

22:47.617 --> 22:48.937
to advise and guide me often

22:49.377 --> 22:50.897
and help me stabilize the court.

22:51.256 --> 22:52.016
What say you?

22:57.736 --> 22:58.536
Your Majesty,

23:00.056 --> 23:00.977
I

23:02.016 --> 23:04.776
appreciate your trust and esteem.

23:05.417 --> 23:06.576
However,

23:07.377 --> 23:09.177
this old frame of mine

23:10.457 --> 23:13.256
has been weary
in both heart and strength.

23:13.736 --> 23:16.576
I am afraid I can no longer bear
the heavy burdens of the court.

23:17.977 --> 23:21.657
Nowadays, there are many
capable officials in the court.

23:21.937 --> 23:23.617
People like valiant Prince Ding

23:24.096 --> 23:25.937
and capable Gu Zheng

23:26.857 --> 23:29.177
can all share Your Majesty's burdens.

23:30.576 --> 23:32.657
What Your Majesty must do

23:33.617 --> 23:35.256
is to use the wise and able

23:35.776 --> 23:37.137
and gather collective wisdom

23:38.536 --> 23:41.496
to overcome
the difficult times together.

23:58.937 --> 23:59.617
Your Highness,

23:59.937 --> 24:01.576
look. Aren't they beautiful?

24:09.056 --> 24:10.016
Where is this place?

24:10.937 --> 24:13.217
I was in the carriage
the entire way here.

24:13.496 --> 24:15.256
I have almost lost
all sense of direction.

24:15.897 --> 24:17.096
This is Qingshi Township.

24:18.536 --> 24:19.897
Qingshi Township?

24:21.736 --> 24:22.857
I have never heard of it.

24:24.977 --> 24:26.776
Just a small, remote border town.

24:29.536 --> 24:30.617
Not many households here.

24:31.137 --> 24:33.096
The land is not very fertile either.

24:33.897 --> 24:34.736
In earlier years,

24:35.096 --> 24:36.496
there was once a jade mine here.

24:36.736 --> 24:37.937
It drew quite a lot of people.

24:38.697 --> 24:39.417
Later,

24:40.137 --> 24:41.736
the jade was nearly all mined out,

24:42.016 --> 24:43.137
so it was abandoned.

24:43.816 --> 24:46.177
Even the official roads
and posthouse built at that time

24:46.457 --> 24:47.256
have also

24:48.496 --> 24:49.657
been abandoned by now.

24:51.576 --> 24:53.617
How does Your Highness
know all this so clearly?

24:55.937 --> 24:56.977
Because this is

24:58.496 --> 24:59.697
my mom's hometown.

25:03.776 --> 25:05.256
She was born and raised here.

25:06.096 --> 25:07.336
As she played the guqin well

25:07.816 --> 25:09.256
and had some good looks,

25:09.977 --> 25:11.217
she was sent into the palace

25:11.336 --> 25:12.256
as a palace maid.

25:13.217 --> 25:14.217
By chance,

25:14.937 --> 25:16.256
she gained my father's favor

25:16.697 --> 25:17.736
and gave birth to me.

25:19.617 --> 25:21.617
She must have been
a very wonderful woman.

25:24.217 --> 25:25.056
Wonderful?

25:27.016 --> 25:27.937
I actually

25:30.137 --> 25:31.217
don't remember much.

25:31.977 --> 25:33.937
She passed away
when I was four years old.

25:40.217 --> 25:41.776
I grew up in the Eastern Palace.

25:42.496 --> 25:43.776
Although I was a prince,

25:44.457 --> 25:46.377
even the lowliest servants

25:46.816 --> 25:48.137
could humiliate me at will.

25:49.736 --> 25:50.536
Later,

25:51.377 --> 25:52.776
I thought of a way.

25:53.536 --> 25:55.897
If I could become
the disciple of a powerful

25:56.256 --> 25:57.736
and renowned master,

25:58.417 --> 25:59.937
and with him as my backing,

26:00.576 --> 26:01.377
my days

26:01.776 --> 26:03.056
might become easier to bear.

26:04.816 --> 26:05.937
So,

26:06.657 --> 26:07.897
I begged my father

26:08.177 --> 26:09.977
to send me to Lishan to recuperate.

26:10.536 --> 26:11.496
In reality,

26:12.457 --> 26:14.256
I wanted to become
Headmaster Xu's disciple.

26:18.657 --> 26:20.697
But Headmaster Xu refused to accept me.

26:21.937 --> 26:23.457
He was such a wise man.

26:23.977 --> 26:24.776
He must have

26:25.977 --> 26:27.816
seen through me at a single glance.

26:44.016 --> 26:44.816
Fortunately,

26:45.897 --> 26:47.296
I quickly found another way,

26:48.096 --> 26:48.937
Li.

26:51.377 --> 26:53.217
Li is Headmaster Xu's own granddaughter.

26:53.816 --> 26:55.137
If I could marry her,

26:55.776 --> 26:56.736
the entire Lishan

26:57.056 --> 26:58.496
would stand behind me.

27:02.336 --> 27:03.536
At that time, Li

27:04.296 --> 27:06.377
was still a naive
and innocent little girl.

27:07.336 --> 27:08.816
With just a few small tricks,

27:09.336 --> 27:11.217
I easily gained her trust.

27:12.937 --> 27:14.056
She treated me very well,

27:15.177 --> 27:16.576
so I wrote to my father

27:16.977 --> 27:18.177
and requested the marriage.

27:21.217 --> 27:22.496
At that time, my father

27:22.776 --> 27:24.857
was in a life-and-death struggle
with Guo Jin.

27:25.576 --> 27:26.377
Presumably,

27:27.217 --> 27:28.736
he also coveted the power of Lishan.

27:29.336 --> 27:30.137
The marriage

27:30.816 --> 27:31.857
was very easily arranged.

27:33.496 --> 27:34.296
Li probably

27:35.937 --> 27:37.776
still doesn't know all this to this day.

27:41.977 --> 27:42.776
See?

27:43.816 --> 27:46.016
I am just this kind of cold-hearted,

27:46.657 --> 27:47.937
calculating person.

27:50.457 --> 27:51.776
I calculated people's hearts,

27:52.296 --> 27:53.377
calculated the benefits,

27:53.697 --> 27:55.697
and calculated every move
on the chessboard.

27:58.336 --> 27:59.736
But I simply didn't calculate

28:00.977 --> 28:02.977
that amidst all these schemes,

28:03.977 --> 28:05.377
I lost my own heart.

28:08.897 --> 28:10.016
I fell in love with her.

28:16.897 --> 28:18.056
What I expected even less

28:19.816 --> 28:22.056
was that my aloof and lofty father

28:22.576 --> 28:24.096
would fall from power so early,

28:24.897 --> 28:27.496
perishing in that towering inferno,

28:28.377 --> 28:30.576
causing my entire game to fall apart.

28:41.937 --> 28:42.576
I'm sorry

28:43.377 --> 28:44.576
to let you hear all this,

28:45.137 --> 28:46.096
adding to your pain.

28:47.657 --> 28:48.457
No,

28:50.536 --> 28:51.576
I am very glad

28:52.256 --> 28:54.296
that Your Highness
would share your heart with me.

28:56.336 --> 28:57.736
You really are a silly girl.

29:00.377 --> 29:01.857
You shouldn't have come to my side,

29:02.617 --> 29:03.377
let alone

29:03.897 --> 29:05.736
be dragged
into the bottomless whirlpool.

29:07.016 --> 29:08.336
I have never been good to you.

29:09.137 --> 29:10.576
I am not a good person, either.

29:11.056 --> 29:11.897
In the end,

29:13.137 --> 29:14.736
I have brought you to this sorry state,

29:16.056 --> 29:17.617
yet I can't compensate you at all.

29:18.496 --> 29:19.296
No,

29:20.657 --> 29:21.977
Your Highness has not harmed me.

29:24.016 --> 29:25.377
It was my own choice.

29:26.457 --> 29:28.177
I chose to follow Your Highness.

29:30.417 --> 29:32.217
I don't want riches and titles.

29:32.576 --> 29:35.096
Nor do I want grand mansions
or other estates.

29:37.417 --> 29:39.776
I only want to be
with Your Highness forever.

29:43.336 --> 29:44.137
From now on,

29:44.776 --> 29:46.177
let us live here

29:46.776 --> 29:48.536
in Your Highness's mom's hometown.

29:49.977 --> 29:51.736
We can farm together

29:52.857 --> 29:54.657
or run a small business together.

29:56.857 --> 29:58.296
I have learned how to grow flowers.

29:58.897 --> 30:00.857
We can tend a field of flowers together.

30:01.857 --> 30:03.816
I'll always be by Your Highness's side.

30:05.016 --> 30:05.816
Always.

30:07.296 --> 30:08.096
Forever.

30:13.977 --> 30:15.056
A person like me

30:16.016 --> 30:18.056
was born to struggle against fate.

30:19.336 --> 30:20.937
Once I set foot on this path,

30:22.096 --> 30:23.536
there is no turning back.

30:35.296 --> 30:36.016
Your Highness,

30:36.016 --> 30:37.296
- don't make me leave.
- My lady.

30:37.296 --> 30:37.897
- Your Highness.
- Don't go.

30:37.897 --> 30:38.816
I'm begging you!

30:38.816 --> 30:39.336
Let me go!

30:39.657 --> 30:40.417
- Let me go!
- My lady!

30:40.417 --> 30:41.617
- What are you doing?
- Your Highness!

30:41.617 --> 30:42.857
Your Highness, don't go!

30:43.256 --> 30:43.977
- Let me go!
- Your Highness!

30:51.977 --> 30:53.536
I am the one who let you down.

30:55.256 --> 30:56.776
If fate allows it in the future,

30:57.576 --> 30:59.096
we may perhaps meet again.

31:00.137 --> 31:01.417
If our fate is truly exhausted,

31:04.217 --> 31:06.296
then live the rest of your life well.

31:07.096 --> 31:08.496
I don't want that, Your Highness.

31:08.496 --> 31:10.016
Your Highness! Your Highness!

31:10.016 --> 31:11.377
- Don't go, Your Highness!
- My lady!

31:11.377 --> 31:13.056
Your Highness, don't go!

31:13.056 --> 31:14.816
- Let me go!
- Let go!

31:14.816 --> 31:16.177
- Your Highness!
- Let go!

31:16.177 --> 31:17.657
- Your Highness!
- My lady!

31:17.657 --> 31:19.056
Let go of me!

31:19.417 --> 31:20.656
- Your Highness!
- Let go!

31:20.816 --> 31:21.488
Let go!

31:21.488 --> 31:22.857
- Your Highness!
- Let go now!

31:23.217 --> 31:24.736
- Your Highness!
- Let go!

31:25.096 --> 31:26.617
- Let me go!
- Let go!

31:26.864 --> 31:28.457
- Your Highness!
- My lady!

31:29.937 --> 31:31.217
- My lady!
- Your Highness!

31:31.697 --> 31:32.576
My lady.

31:38.857 --> 31:40.816
Her Majesty has arrived!

31:45.857 --> 31:46.697
Yanqi.

31:47.576 --> 31:48.857
I'm discussing state affairs.

31:49.657 --> 31:50.657
Please return, Mother.

32:09.576 --> 32:10.576
The hour is approaching.

32:11.336 --> 32:12.496
I must go to court now.

32:13.536 --> 32:14.496
State affairs are heavy.

32:15.256 --> 32:16.056
Later,

32:16.576 --> 32:17.897
I'll go pay you my respects.

32:39.296 --> 32:40.256
Your Majesty,

32:40.857 --> 32:43.736
Prince Ding's army has reclaimed
Yunzhou and Shuozhou

32:44.096 --> 32:45.417
and crushed the rebels.

32:45.417 --> 32:47.056
They'll return in triumph soon.

32:47.417 --> 32:50.177
This is the kind of victory
we haven't had for a long time.

32:55.336 --> 32:56.657
Prince Ding is valiant.

32:56.857 --> 32:58.697
He is truly the pillar of the state.

32:59.617 --> 33:00.417
Indeed.

33:00.536 --> 33:03.377
Prince Ding has not failed
the heavy trust of Your Majesty.

33:03.657 --> 33:05.776
He's truly a blessing for the nation.

33:06.417 --> 33:07.977
He hasn't disappointed my hopes.

33:08.496 --> 33:09.336
He shall be rewarded.

33:10.377 --> 33:12.736
Prince Ding, Mo Xiuyao,
is hereby granted an honorary title.

33:12.977 --> 33:15.296
His sister-in-law, Ms. Wen,
is titled State Lady.

33:15.336 --> 33:16.256
Mo Wuyou

33:16.336 --> 33:18.417
is restored to the imperial clan
and re-ennobled.

33:18.697 --> 33:19.857
Princess Ding, Ye Li,

33:19.857 --> 33:21.296
is titled First-Rank Princess

33:21.457 --> 33:22.857
and bestowed 1,000 bolts of silk.

33:23.256 --> 33:24.217
In five days,

33:24.336 --> 33:26.857
from Danque Avenue
to the Imperial Way at Chengtian Gate,

33:27.016 --> 33:29.016
let there be performances and lanterns

33:29.217 --> 33:30.536
to welcome Prince Ding's return.

33:31.457 --> 33:33.217
- Your Majesty is wise.
- Your Majesty is wise.

33:36.377 --> 33:37.336
Everyone!

33:37.336 --> 33:39.177
Fellow townsmen!

33:39.336 --> 33:42.377
Today is not only a joyous day
for our Prince Ding's Mansion

33:42.377 --> 33:44.656
but also a joyous day for our country.

33:44.656 --> 33:47.056
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

33:54.457 --> 33:56.296
Let us share the joy!

33:56.296 --> 33:57.377
Hand out the candies.

33:57.377 --> 33:58.417
Everyone, share the joy.

33:58.417 --> 34:00.977
Come on, everyone, share the joy.

34:04.576 --> 34:05.377
Come on.

34:23.347 --> 34:23.856
Halt.

34:24.656 --> 34:25.520
Show me the papers.

34:25.616 --> 34:26.148
Alright.

34:26.576 --> 34:27.180
Go on.

34:27.472 --> 34:28.015
Yes.

34:51.952 --> 34:52.848
Your Highness.

34:55.337 --> 34:56.377
All set?

34:56.656 --> 34:57.216
Your Highness,

34:57.377 --> 34:58.737
fire oil has arrived in bulk,

34:58.737 --> 35:00.337
and the kindling's ready too.

35:00.337 --> 35:01.777
They are hidden and concealed.

35:04.496 --> 35:06.257
What about the men
we left in the capital?

35:06.496 --> 35:07.857
They are all standing by.

35:08.176 --> 35:08.977
In three days,

35:08.977 --> 35:11.176
the lantern festival
to welcome Prince Ding will begin.

35:11.176 --> 35:12.257
And in four days,

35:12.656 --> 35:13.897
Prince Ding will return.

35:14.777 --> 35:16.136
We will act in three days.

35:17.417 --> 35:17.968
Yes.

35:19.257 --> 35:19.937
At that time,

35:19.977 --> 35:22.576
the city's troops will surely
be pulled to maintain order.

35:22.777 --> 35:24.096
Once the city falls into chaos,

35:24.417 --> 35:26.977
that will be the time for our operation.

35:27.056 --> 35:27.857
Good.

35:29.016 --> 35:30.096
In three days,

35:30.737 --> 35:33.016
let's rise in the chaos,
storm the imperial city,

35:33.576 --> 35:35.737
and take the little emperor's life!

35:36.056 --> 35:37.737
For the blood of the Eastern Palace,

35:38.016 --> 35:39.056
justice must be served!

35:50.496 --> 35:51.737
Looking to buy something, sir?

35:53.136 --> 35:54.056
Is Ye Li here?

35:54.616 --> 35:55.857
You are our shop owner's?

35:56.937 --> 35:58.576
I was previously a clerk here.

35:59.576 --> 36:00.337
A clerk?

36:06.777 --> 36:07.440
She is not here.

36:07.440 --> 36:09.417
We are closed.
Please come back tomorrow.

36:12.977 --> 36:13.777
My lady,

36:14.176 --> 36:14.977
let's go.

36:22.352 --> 36:23.472
(Shende Shop)

36:28.737 --> 36:29.777
Yusheng.

36:31.457 --> 36:32.136
Waiting long?

36:32.457 --> 36:33.136
Are you hungry?

36:33.737 --> 36:34.777
Let's go eat something.

36:35.016 --> 36:35.777
Alright.

36:51.297 --> 36:52.977
Red Fox, lead ten squads of guards

36:53.096 --> 36:55.176
to set fires on the major streets
of the capital.

36:55.257 --> 36:56.977
Throw the entire city into chaos

36:56.977 --> 36:58.536
within the shortest time possible.

36:59.376 --> 36:59.937
Understood.

37:00.777 --> 37:03.656
We have our own men at Changxing Gate.

37:04.297 --> 37:06.096
They will poison
the other guards tonight

37:06.257 --> 37:08.377
and ensure Changxing Gate
remains sealed shut tonight

37:08.696 --> 37:10.056
to prevent the three battalions

37:10.056 --> 37:13.457
from getting word of the fire
and coming to the palace's aid.

37:14.176 --> 37:15.297
At the stroke of midnight,

37:15.616 --> 37:17.496
His Highness will lead
the most loyal warriors

37:17.656 --> 37:19.696
to storm the imperial palace
together with us

37:19.937 --> 37:24.080
and slay the wretched Empress Guo Jin
and the child emperor, Mo Yanqi.

37:29.656 --> 37:30.937
Win or lose, rise or fall,

37:31.897 --> 37:33.297
all rests on this one move.

37:34.096 --> 37:36.496
We may not see tomorrow's sunrise.

37:37.417 --> 37:39.216
None of us may survive.

37:40.337 --> 37:42.457
But we will use their lives

37:43.536 --> 37:45.176
to avenge my father and brother

37:46.337 --> 37:48.536
and honor the loyal souls
of the Eastern Palace.

37:55.897 --> 37:56.817
Your Highness.

37:57.377 --> 37:58.257
Your Highness.

38:00.377 --> 38:01.897
Can't you just not go?

38:03.977 --> 38:05.817
Just take Her Highness and leave.

38:06.977 --> 38:08.897
Find some place where no one knows you

38:08.977 --> 38:10.257
and live a peaceful life.

38:10.696 --> 38:11.496
Or...

38:12.457 --> 38:14.032
or if you don't like Her Highness,

38:14.377 --> 38:15.457
just leave on your own.

38:16.136 --> 38:18.417
The world is vast.
There's always a place for you.

38:19.496 --> 38:20.777
Whether you are an emperor,

38:21.176 --> 38:22.257
a prince,

38:22.777 --> 38:24.176
or just a commoner,

38:25.457 --> 38:27.417
you will always be my lord.

38:32.417 --> 38:35.096
I just want you to live well.

38:37.096 --> 38:38.216
I'm begging you.

38:45.616 --> 38:46.417
Qingbao,

38:47.016 --> 38:47.977
let go of me.

38:48.136 --> 38:49.377
Don't try to stop me.

38:56.417 --> 38:58.480
I haven't lived like a man.

39:00.496 --> 39:01.737
At least when I die,

39:04.096 --> 39:06.016
I can die as a man.

39:09.536 --> 39:11.297
Then let me stay with Your Highness.

39:12.056 --> 39:13.176
On the road to death,

39:14.337 --> 39:16.096
I can still hold a lantern for you.

39:25.337 --> 39:26.417
Silly Qingbao,

39:29.216 --> 39:31.257
you have to live to collect my body.

39:34.136 --> 39:34.817
And also,

39:40.417 --> 39:42.096
remember to find that little girl.

39:43.576 --> 39:44.457
She won't survive

39:45.457 --> 39:46.297
on her own.

39:48.417 --> 39:49.656
Take care of her for me,

39:49.656 --> 39:50.417
will you?

39:57.417 --> 39:58.257
Your Highness!

39:59.297 --> 40:00.176
Your Highness!

40:56.337 --> 40:57.576
Bravo!

40:57.576 --> 40:58.696
Mom, come here.

40:58.696 --> 40:59.737
There's a fire-breather!

40:59.737 --> 41:00.297
Hurry!

41:03.496 --> 41:04.216
Be careful.

41:04.216 --> 41:05.297
Stay away from the fire.

41:06.897 --> 41:08.297
They are so amazing.

41:09.377 --> 41:11.056
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

41:11.417 --> 41:13.977
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

41:14.576 --> 41:16.257
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

41:16.377 --> 41:17.417
Amazing!

41:17.457 --> 41:18.417
This lantern festival

41:18.536 --> 41:20.136
is truly unprecedented in its grandeur.

41:20.576 --> 41:21.257
It's wonderful.

41:21.656 --> 41:22.857
The last time it was so lively

41:23.656 --> 41:25.937
was in the first year of Jinghe,
when Huaixi was pacified

41:27.136 --> 41:28.777
and the late emperor granted amnesty

41:29.496 --> 41:31.897
and held a lantern festival
to welcome Heiyun Cavalry back.

41:33.656 --> 41:34.457
If only

41:34.897 --> 41:36.616
Xiuwen could see this day...

41:36.616 --> 41:37.337
Ms. Wen.

41:39.257 --> 41:40.457
Let's not talk about it.

41:40.457 --> 41:41.977
This should be a happy day.

41:42.257 --> 41:42.897
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

41:44.937 --> 41:45.737
Indeed.

41:46.096 --> 41:47.417
If only they could see it.

41:50.417 --> 41:51.656
Fire!

41:56.857 --> 41:57.817
Move aside!

41:59.096 --> 42:00.056
- Move aside!
- Make way!

42:00.136 --> 42:00.817
Fire over there!

42:00.817 --> 42:01.712
Fire!

42:01.712 --> 42:02.337
Run!

42:09.096 --> 42:10.737
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

42:10.977 --> 42:11.616
Let's go.

42:11.616 --> 42:12.417
Truly amazing.

42:13.576 --> 42:14.216
Fire!

42:14.216 --> 42:14.937
Don't go there!

42:14.937 --> 42:15.696
Fire!

42:17.257 --> 42:18.977
Take Ms. Wen and Wuyou
back to the mansion.

42:19.216 --> 42:20.457
Aren't you coming with us?

42:20.897 --> 42:22.176
I'll go see what's happening.

42:22.176 --> 42:23.176
Don't worry, Ms. Wen.

42:23.176 --> 42:24.136
I have shadow guards.

42:24.937 --> 42:26.176
Then you must be careful.

42:27.457 --> 42:28.136
Go ahead.

42:32.777 --> 42:33.377
Fire!

42:33.377 --> 42:34.377
Fire!

42:37.016 --> 42:37.777
Fire!

42:37.857 --> 42:38.616
Fire!

42:40.599 --> 42:43.856
(Preview)

42:43.977 --> 42:45.457
Do you want to be emperor that badly?

42:45.656 --> 42:47.297
So many people have died in the city

42:47.897 --> 42:49.056
and the streets run red.

42:49.297 --> 42:51.257
Are you, who treat the people as weeds,

42:51.536 --> 42:53.096
fit to rule the realm?

42:53.297 --> 42:54.136
Li.

42:54.777 --> 42:55.280
Run!

42:58.656 --> 43:00.096
At this point,

43:00.496 --> 43:02.977
nothing and no one
in this world can stop me.

43:03.096 --> 43:03.897
Not

43:04.176 --> 43:04.977
even you!

43:05.257 --> 43:06.337
Order the vanguard

43:07.096 --> 43:07.977
to enter the city.

43:14.736 --> 43:21.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:24.912 --> 43:31.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:33.264 --> 43:36.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:36.720 --> 43:42.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:43.056 --> 43:46.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:46.544 --> 43:53.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:54.160 --> 43:58.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:58.096 --> 44:03.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:04.304 --> 44:12.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:13.808 --> 44:19.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:19.312 --> 44:24.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:24.880 --> 44:28.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:29.232 --> 44:34.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:35.056 --> 44:38.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:38.800 --> 44:44.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:45.232 --> 44:53.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:54.608 --> 44:59.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:00.112 --> 45:06.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:06.016 --> 45:10.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:10.352 --> 45:15.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:16.304 --> 45:20.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:20.816 --> 45:26.256
♪Unbound by form♪
